narrative.title: Provider Overview
narrative.text: Freedom Management is a Community/Behavioral Health provider based in Russell Springs, KY. From the 2018–2024 period, this provider received $13.3M in Medicaid payments across 116K claims.

narrative.title: Why This Matters
narrative.text: At $13.3M in Medicaid payments, this provider represents significant public healthcare spending. Understanding where these dollars go helps ensure the program serves those who need it most.
